cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on modeling the spatial co-occurrence of neuron responses in deep convolutional neural networks for visual recognition. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper borrows the idea of Bag-of-Visual-Words (BoVW) model, which is commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
